text:
Very glad to see that China did not blink.  Add this reversal to the growing list of broken campaign promises that Trump is accumulating:  

Hillary locked up, nope;  
Wall Street out of politics, big nope; 
draining the swamp; nope; 
Muslim ban, big nope; 
separating personal/family business and politics, big nope.  

At some point his supporters will realise they have been hoodwinked.
